aculty" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">aka.ms/BCEforEDUFaculty</a>和<a href="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/microsoft-365-blog/bing-chat-enterprise-faq/bc-p/3880944" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">Bing Chat Enterprise FAQ</a>来了解更多信息。</p> ; 
